[30;1m16 | [0m[35mdef batched(iterable: Iterable[T], n: int) -> Iterable[tuple[T, ...]]:[0m
[30;1m17 | [0m[35m    # batched('ABCDEFG', 3) --> ABC DEF G[0m
[30;1m18 | [0m[35m    if n < 1:[0m
[30;1m19 | [0m[35m        raise ValueError("n must be at least one")[0m
[30;1m20 | [0m[35m    it = iter(iterable)[0m
[30;1m21 | [0m[35m    while batch := tuple(islice(it, n)):[0m
[30;1m22 | [0m[35m        yield batch[0m

[30;1m16 | [0m[35mdef batched(iterable: Iterable[T], n: int) -> Iterable[tuple[T, ...]]:[0m
[30;1m17 | [0m[35m    # batched('ABCDEFG', 3) --> ABC DEF G[0m
[30;1m18 | [0m[35m    if n < 1:[0m
[30;1m19 | [0m[35m        raise ValueError("n must be at least one")[0m
[30;1m20 | [0m[35m    it = iter(iterable)[0m
[30;1m21 | [0m[35m    while batch := tuple(islice(it, n)):[0m
[30;1m22 | [0m[35m        yield batch[0m
